SQL_STMT_U.val: select CAST ( (((CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESAUTO + CMON_TOTADEDUCTCRALLDISC + CMON_TOTADEDUCTCRNOTALLDISC + CMON_TOTADEDUCTCROTHER) * 100) /(CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO)) AS DECIMAL (13,2 )) from :5/CMON where CMON_ADMNO=:2 and CMON_CLNTNO=:1 and CMON_YEAR=:3 and CMON_CURRENCY='PLN' and (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO)>0 and CMON_MONTH <= :4;

select CAST ( sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO) AS DECIMAL ( 13,2) ) from :5/CMON where CMON_ADMNO=:2 and CMON_CLNTNO=:1 and CMON_YEAR=:3 and CMON_CURRENCY='PLN' and CMON_MONTH<=:4;

select CAST ( sum(CMON_TOTIFACTCOMMSCHED + CMON_TOTIFACTCOMMSCHEDADD + CMON_TOTIMINCOMM + CMON_TOTIFIXCOMM ) AS DECIMAL (13 , 2 ) ) from :4/CMON where CMON_ADMNO=:2 and CMON_CLNTNO=:1 and CMON_YEAR=:3 and CMON_CURRENCY='PLN' ;

SELECT CAST ( SUM(CMON_TOTIIFACTDEBIT + CMON_TOTIIFACTCREDIT + CMON_TOTIIFACTSURCHARGEOD + CMON_TOTIICREDCOMM + CMON_TOTIIARRANGEM + CMON_TOTIIARRANGEMCREDCOMM + CMON_TOTIISTOCK + CMON_TOTIISTOCKCREDITCOMM) AS DECIMAL (13,2)) FROM :4/CMON WHERE CMON_ADMNO=:2 and CMON_CLNTNO=:1 and CMON_YEAR=:3 and CMON_CURRENCY='PLN' ;
